<lb ed="C I" n="0121a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>報德玉像七佛頌碑</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0121a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑陰" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑陰</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0121a01"/><p id="pI01p0121a0101">魏報德
<lb ed="C I" n="0121a02"/>玉象七
<lb ed="C I" n="0121a03"/>佛頌碑</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b01"/><p id="pI01p0121b0101"><note n="0121001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">軓＝軌【史】</note><app n="0121001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軓</rdg></app>基綿邈。體非緣待。有&CB07099;不染。唯聖乃<note n="0121002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30760;＝詳【史】</note><app n="0121002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詳</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30760;</rdg></app>實證□以□□□□□□故<note n="0121003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02127;＝夢【史】</note><app n="0121003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02127;</rdg></app>中說
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b02"/><app source="0121003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02127;</rdg></app>。周蝶相轉。或云始從見□終於第一。有思成佛□□□□□□□法身。&CB07099;心
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b03"/>於為<note n="0121004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30768;＝而【史】</note><app n="0121004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">而</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30768;</rdg></app>&CB07099;不為。任物成壞。位極方具。故知山谷之音□□可盡。如<app source="0121003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02127;</rdg></app>所見。非求
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b04"/>可得。一俯一仰。木石開□。況至理之中。何身不有。同□□方。其誰不是。□□三
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b05"/>界。何家知非。&CB07099;在不在。□綸太虛信矣。是以共<note n="0121005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30762;＝世【史】</note><app n="0121005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30762;</rdg></app>人□□歷劫猶不覺知。況業
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b06"/><note n="0121006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB10332;＝差【史】</note><app n="0121006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">差</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB10332;</rdg></app>地別。七識十居。毒飯馬麥。正其宜也。明須結心王□□。佇立門側。時宿<note n="0121007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">艸＝草【史】</note><app n="0121007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">草</lem><rdg wit="【原】">艸</rdg></app>菴。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b07"/>始信是天屬。諒非旦夕之間可得逢覲。涓涓決石。履□堅冰。　大魏龍飛<note n="0121008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30761;＝琚i史】</note><app n="0121008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】"></lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30761;</rdg></app>代。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b08"/><note n="0121009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刱＝創【史】</note><app n="0121009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">創</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刱</rdg></app>基帝業。王有九土。至　高祖孝文。定鼎崧洛。莊飾□宙。津梁四海。禮樂更新。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b09"/>雅頌洋溢。於是逆旅星宮。林墅華殿。廣興塔<note n="0121010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08775;＝廟【史】</note><app n="0121010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08775;</rdg></app>。紹隆三寶。始造報德寺。洸洸濟
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b10"/>濟。與舍衛竹園同風。　宣武皇帝。剖玉荊山。賈重連城。彫鏤瑩飾。模一佛兩菩
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b11"/>薩。石基<note n="0121011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00513;＝磚【史】</note><app n="0121011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">磚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00513;</rdg></app>宮。樹於寺庭。法鼓於是始聞<app source="0121005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30762;</rdg></app>間。中止之輪<note n="0121012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30763;＝再【史】</note><app n="0121012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">再</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30763;</rdg></app>轉於大千。半月之儀。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b12"/>流暉於東夏。寔淪影餘光。亦&CI0003;初旭。沙門曇昌。蒙國慈矜。無由仰謝。共慧雲。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b13"/>洛州刺史田景。車騎將軍<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">姚</unclear>元標。河南太守司馬相貴。□參軍杜文敬等。建碑
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b14"/><note n="0121013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30764;＝前【史】</note><app n="0121013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30764;</rdg></app>像金容。後刊靈讚。庶以茲<note n="0121014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【史】</note><app n="0121014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>。崇增川岳。願　七<note n="0121015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30765;＝廟【史】</note><app n="0121015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30765;</rdg></app><note n="0121016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30766;＝神【史】</note><app n="0121016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">神</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30766;</rdg></app>□□域。皇祚遐隆。群寮
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b15"/>忠貞。曠劫師僧。七<app source="0121005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30762;</rdg></app>父母。法界含識。同霑斯慶。龍華之□。□登初會。其詞曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b16"/>三有深&CB07099;限。彼岸甚悠悠。於中常淪沒。何年見春秋。唯□□力王。水上乘輕舟。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b17"/>汎汎隨波轉。載沈<note n="0121017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30767;＝復【史】</note><app n="0121017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30767;</rdg></app>載浮。意欲渡斯盡。正恨緣廢休。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">願</unclear>□□是者。應當速返流。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b18"/>行藏業不許。樹靜風豈聽。如<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">船</unclear>墮迴<app source="0121017" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30767;</rdg></app>。無由得自亭。□□迺一<note n="0121018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09496;＝散【史】</note><app n="0121018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">散</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09496;</rdg></app>。誰當可盡生。
<lb ed="C I" n="0121b19"/>不如奮雲翼。高翔天中城。　　武定三年歲在乙丑□□丁丑朔十五日建</p>
</div2>
